# Source requirements for the Qwen3.5-4B scene-VLM sidecar venv (Python 3.12).
# transformers==5.3.0 is the load-bearing pin (the openral runtime venv hard-pins
# this for lerobot; the sidecar keeps the 4B+CUDA stack out of the rclpy process).
# Regenerate the lock with:
#   uv pip compile tools/sidecar_requirements/qwen_vlm.in \
#     --universal --torch-backend=cu128 --generate-hashes --python-version 3.12 \
#     -o tools/sidecar_requirements/qwen_vlm.lock
